.Dd May 17, 2026
.Dt DOOMDOTS 1
.Os
.Sh NAME
.Nm doomdots
.Nd DOOMSDAY dotfile module
.Sh DESCRIPTION
.Nm
is the dotfile module for the DOOMSDAY desktop stack. It installs shell, X11,
editor, terminal, browser, media, and helper-script configuration by delegating
to the
.Pa dots
repository Makefile.
.Sh INSTALL
.Dl \&./install.sh --dots
.Sh UNINSTALL
.Dl \&./install.sh --uninstall --dots
.Sh FILES
.Bl -tag -width "$DOTFILES_PREFIX"
.It Pa $DOTFILES_PREFIX
Destination for symlinked dotfiles. Defaults to
.Ev HOME .
.It Pa $BUILD_ROOT/dots
Local checkout of the module repository.
.El
.Sh SEE ALSO
.Xr doomsday-system 1
